WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.960 --> 00:00:05.840
Marriage, as I told you, is a
divine work.

00:00:05.840 --> 00:00:13.600
It's the work for the balancing
of human beings.

00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:16.800
When you get married, you
definitely develop a balance

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:20.080
in life, and a control over
yourself.

00:00:20.080 --> 00:00:24.480
But one must understand that
if you marry in Sahaja Yoga,

00:00:24.480 --> 00:00:28.960
then you are marrying in real
religion, not in an artificial way.

00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:32.880
And you have lots of
responsibilities as married people.

00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:36.400
One of them is, the greatest of
all is, that you should not be

00:00:36.400 --> 00:00:39.840
unfaithful to each other
anymore.

00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:45.120
Fidelity is the basis of
married life.

00:00:45.120 --> 00:00:48.320
Complete fidelity should be
given to each other.

00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:52.160
And once this faith is broken,
then there is no end

00:00:52.160 --> 00:00:57.120
to this derailment.
So the first basis is fidelity.

00:00:57.120 --> 00:01:02.480
Because you are married in
Sahaja Yoga, and a Sahaja Yogini

00:01:02.480 --> 00:01:08.000
and a Sahaja Yogi, it is very
important that we must understand

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:14.960
that once we lose the principle
of marriage, we cannot have happiness.

00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:20.880
You know that in the West, how
people have played with

00:01:20.880 --> 00:01:23.440
this great institution of
marriage.

00:01:23.440 --> 00:01:30.800
And now even in the East, in
India also, people are doing the same.

00:01:30.800 --> 00:01:35.120
But for us, it is important to
understand our responsibility

00:01:35.120 --> 00:01:42.720
as married people.
Try to find out good points

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:51.040
of each other, and not the
mistakes or the loopholes in them.

00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:59.040
Try to glorify your companion.
By that you will improve.

00:01:59.040 --> 00:02:03.120
And don't try to pull the
person down by finding

00:02:03.120 --> 00:02:09.840
all the faults all the time.
As you know, I love you very much,

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:13.920
despite your faults. In the
same way, you have to love

00:02:13.920 --> 00:02:18.320
each other despite each other's
faults.

00:02:18.320 --> 00:02:23.440
There should be no domination
between the two persons.

00:02:23.440 --> 00:02:25.840
That is very important to
understand.

00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:32.080
But husband has his own role,
and wife has her own sweet role.

00:02:32.080 --> 00:02:35.120
Marriage has to be made
successful in Sahaja Yoga.

00:02:35.120 --> 00:02:40.160
It's very important. Because
of this institution being

00:02:40.160 --> 00:02:46.960
completely challenged and
damaged, all our societies

00:02:46.960 --> 00:02:51.040
are getting ruined.
You must respect it as a temple,

00:02:51.040 --> 00:02:56.480
that you are building.
And be careful when you deal

00:02:56.480 --> 00:03:00.320
with it in a cheapish way, or
in an analytical way.

00:03:00.320 --> 00:03:01.760
You cannot analyse your
marriage.

00:03:01.760 --> 00:03:03.280
You have no business to
analyse it.

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:06.880
You have to accept it as it is,
go ahead with it.

00:03:06.880 --> 00:03:10.320
Otherwise, if you want to marry
without my consent, you can go ahead.

00:03:10.320 --> 00:03:14.080
But if you have taken my
consent, then please know

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:16.320
that you have to respect your
marriage.

00:03:16.320 --> 00:03:19.360
Then respect your in-laws.
Respect your father-in-law

00:03:19.360 --> 00:03:22.320
and mother-in-law.
Respect your family.

00:03:22.320 --> 00:03:26.000
It is not marriage of two
persons, as you have like

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:28.640
contracts between two persons.
It's the marriage of the whole

00:03:28.640 --> 00:03:32.400
society, of the whole family,
of everyone.

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:35.360
And you have to bring in more
people closer together

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:39.520
with love and affection.
And we have to show that

00:03:39.520 --> 00:03:42.240
within us, the religion is
born now.

00:03:42.240 --> 00:03:46.640
And through that religion, we
are going to spread this

00:03:46.640 --> 00:03:49.200
beautiful, joyous feeling.

00:03:49.200 --> 00:03:55.120
I hope this marriage will bring
greater glory to Sahaja Yoga

00:03:55.120 --> 00:04:00.800
and that you'll abide by the
beautiful maryadas we have,

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:04.720
the boundaries we have, which
we cannot cross.

00:04:04.720 --> 00:04:08.160
May God bless you all.

00:04:14.480 --> 00:04:18.360
You can translate to them what
I've said.

00:04:18.360 --> 00:04:19.600
[Laughter]

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:26.920
Laurent can you say it or
Guillemette.

00:04:26.920 --> 00:04:30.720
Try. And the gentleman who was
organising this program,

00:04:30.720 --> 00:04:34.800
his house, in the front, was
completely blasted

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:38.400
by a thunderbolt.
And he said, "Thank God the

00:04:38.400 --> 00:04:42.640
front was blasted, because I
had renewed the lawn, maximum".

00:04:42.640 --> 00:04:44.160
[Laughter]

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:48.640
But the worst part is, he said
that, "It must be the action

00:04:48.640 --> 00:04:51.600
of some devil who must have
done this".

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:54.400
So the newspaper people say,
"But so far we always had

00:04:54.400 --> 00:05:02.800
learned that thunderbolt comes
from God".

00:05:14.360 --> 00:05:15.360
[Laughter]

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:21.360
And there are two more
incidents where the organizers,

00:05:21.360 --> 00:05:27.120
you see, got into very bad
accident because of thunderbolt.

00:05:27.120 --> 00:05:30.000
So they also said that, "It
must be the devil's work

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:32.560
that they are trying to
trouble us like this,

00:05:32.560 --> 00:05:42.320
through thunderbolt".
They have always used it

00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:49.120
in the wrong way. Like in
Nepal, when they were building

00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:52.720
these horrible temples, you
see, covering them with these

00:05:52.720 --> 00:05:59.280
erotic – what you call- the
statues, they didn't know

00:05:59.280 --> 00:06:02.320
how to explain to the artist
to do this work for a temple,

00:06:02.320 --> 00:06:05.600
you see, outside the temple.
So they said that, "The thunderbolt

00:06:05.600 --> 00:06:08.320
is a virgin, you know,
Vishnumaya is a virgin.

00:06:08.320 --> 00:06:12.080
So if you put such a thing on
top, she will never come near you.

00:06:12.080 --> 00:06:17.600
So it's better to put such
things on top of the temple

00:06:17.600 --> 00:06:20.480
so that they will never be
destroyed". Because they were

00:06:20.480 --> 00:06:29.120
all made out of wood. This was
the argument given for thunderbolt.

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:33.120
Wonderful human brains, I must
say. They know how to-

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:42.880
did you follow the point, what
they said?

00:06:42.880 --> 00:06:50.000
You were the bridesmaid? What
were you doing in the marriage?

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:52.320
Now when you will have the real
marriage, we'll make you

00:06:52.320 --> 00:06:54.880
the flower girls, all right?
We'll have Sahaja Yoga marriage

00:06:54.880 --> 00:06:59.840
also. You'll become the flower
girl then, all right?

00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:08.880
You'll become the flower girl
also.

00:07:08.880 --> 00:07:12.708
Mother, I had seven bridesmaids
today.

00:07:12.708 --> 00:07:12.712
Hum?

00:07:12.712 --> 00:07:15.840
Mother, I had seven bridesmaids
today.

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:17.743
[Shri Mataji is laughing]

00:07:17.743 --> 00:07:18.400
Nice spontaneous happening.

00:07:18.400 --> 00:07:19.027
Seven?

00:07:19.027 --> 00:07:19.520
[Shri Mataji is laughing]

00:07:19.520 --> 00:07:21.920
Who are they? Who are the
seven bridesmaids, stand up.

00:07:21.920 --> 00:07:23.840
Bridesmaids, raise the hands.

00:07:23.840 --> 00:07:25.360
Sharon.

00:07:25.360 --> 00:07:26.880
Elana is gone.

00:07:26.880 --> 00:07:27.508
Most of them are bridesmaids.

00:07:27.508 --> 00:07:28.480
[In French: There was Marie
also.]

00:07:29.040 --> 00:07:32.064
Elana went home. She had to go
to work.

00:07:32.064 --> 00:07:32.080
Elana went home.

00:07:32.080 --> 00:07:40.160
She's very sorry to miss you.
Elana was a bridesmaid.

00:07:40.160 --> 00:07:42.880
Elana was. You were also.

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:45.520
Yes.

00:07:45.520 --> 00:07:54.800
That's good. All this is so
nice and so joyous.

00:07:59.040 --> 00:08:03.840
So what's the plan? They
haven't published the place

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:07.920
as Porchester Road? Or
Porchester Hall, anything?

00:08:07.920 --> 00:08:10.160
Is Mother on the posters?

00:08:10.160 --> 00:08:13.760
Posters is there, but not on
the newspaper.

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:21.440
So what do you say?

00:08:21.440 --> 00:08:22.560
They'll find it.

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:27.120
No, they'll find it, it's all
right, but I don't know.

00:08:27.120 --> 00:08:46.800
It seems to be a funny
newspaper.

00:08:46.800 --> 00:08:50.640
So you went to the- how was
the marriage done?

00:08:50.640 --> 00:08:52.560
In the registry office.

00:08:52.560 --> 00:08:53.193
Registry office.

00:08:53.193 --> 00:08:56.000
It was nice. He was a nice
man. He's the chief registrar.

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:56.960
What did he say?

00:08:56.960 --> 00:09:02.560
He said how enjoyed he was to
be there and to do the ceremony

00:09:02.560 --> 00:09:06.560
for us. And then he said, "Now
you can talk now, why are

00:09:06.560 --> 00:09:09.120
you all so quiet?" And there
was about 50 people sitting

00:09:09.120 --> 00:09:11.200
around, and they were just
sitting in meditation,

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:13.200
absolutely quiet in meditation.

